## Brute Force
* Brute-Force is the action of of force through applications though constant attacks to the user device, it relates to Kerckhoffs's principle that states that the security of a cryptosystem must lie in the choice of its keys only

# Conclusion
Networking and Security is the core foundation of a well oil business machine. You have to be ale to communicate to people and what a better way than via internet. Where people from all walks of life share information, and personal data over the web, it makes everyone neighbors by the click of a button. You have to have security as well and if you're going to share personal data, it has to be encrypted, as you would'nt want valuable information leaked out.
